### See https://vite.dev/guide/env-and-mode for details on .env file loading

### URL of Vbrick Rev tenant
VITE_VBRICK_URL="https://company.rev.vbrick.com"
### Video ID to load on example page
VITE_VIDEO_ID="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"

### RECOMMENDED! enter in Vbrick account id. Otherwise it will be automatically grabbed from Vbrick in extra API call
VITE_VBRICK_ACCOUNT_ID="00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"

### View Context used in analytics reporting
VITE_VIEW_CONTEXT="Vite"